      <title>两名美联储官员称2020年政策指引缺乏灵活性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/two-fed-officials-say-2020-policy-guidance-lacked-flexibility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒(Christopher Waller)和美联储高级政策顾问简·伊里格(Jane Ihrig)表示，美联储官员在疫情期间的指导可能缺乏足够的灵活性，无法足够快地应对快速上升的通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/two-fed-officials-say-2020-policy-guidance-lacked-flexibility</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 16:00:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
